column2: SELECT up_id, dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) as objId FROM #upload WHERE dbo.fGetNearestObjIdEq(up_ra,up_dec,#) IS NOT NULL EXEC spExecuteSQL &&&'&&&+ cast(x.objId as varchar(#)) + &&&&&& as objID, p.ra, p.dec, p.type, p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z, FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID WHERE p.modelMag_u># and p.modelMag_u<# and p.modelMag_g># and p.modelMag_g<# and p.modelMag_r># and p.modelMag_r<# and p.modelMag_z># and p.modelMag_z<# ORDER by x.up_id &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
